Description:
No annotation on the evelope.
Envelope addressed to "Herrn Prof. Dr. H. G. Evers 61. Darmstadt Kunstgeschichte Institut der T. H." and dated 02.03.67

  • Correspondence with Bruno Lohse (dated 1967) about 'Lot and His Daughters'

The inventory of 1993 also mentions black and white photographs of Lot and His Daughters, but these are missing and were probably taken out in the Rubenianum and filed in the Rubens documentation.
